---
title: Turkish-Spiced Beef with Pickled Cabbage and Garlic Toum Sauce
description: In this tasty Turkish-style rice bowl, juicy seared beef gets tossed in spices and rested atop fresh peas and crunchy pickled red cabbage. Enjoy with a classic creamy garlic toum sauce!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/boeuf-a-la-turque-d8b58670.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/turkish-spiced-beef-626fac7c78370cb2ef064337-2549be00.pdf
